description:
This course provides a high-level introduction to the Sinefa solution and a demonstration of the product's core capabilities. It covers application visibility, network quality, shaping and traffic segmentation. The course is around 30 minutes and included some simple quiz questions.

This is a good introduction prior to conducting Sinefa's Technical Training course.
title: Course 1 - Sinefa Product Demonstration
instructors: Chris Siakos, John Bothe, Con Nikolouzakis, John Milionis
